{
  "stem": "9590.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I mentioned, my mother was very much concerned about my education.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, that young lady, Jana Finkiel, with her husband, Motke Finkiel, fled to Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They remained in Kiev.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he volunteered to go to the Russian army to fight the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She remained behind.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At that time, the Germans took the Russian-- the Kiev Jewry and exterminated them in Babi Yar.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] She was the one that was supposedly shot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on top of her were other corpse.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "When things got quiet, she crept out of the corpse, naked, and left.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "As she was walking in the street in Kiev, she saw from far away a policeman.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She went down a side street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the side street, she was afraid that he'll follow her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All of a sudden, she saw an outhouse, AND she jumped in that filth and-- to save her life.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Then she came out of there and went to a-- to a home.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When it got quiet, knocked at the door and asked people to help her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They helped her get washed, and they gave her something to wear.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she came back to her husband parents, to our town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now, my mother was financially in a better position than that family, so she didn't want to hand them down just to share a piece of bread, or whatever she had with them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So she had an idea that she would ask that young lady, Jana Finkiel, to tutor me, to-- to teach me, because she was a university student, and I was still in high school, so that I don't waste the time.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And this way, she'll pay her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it will be a dignified way how to give to help her.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
